{"tid":2321882,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【台灣】港人居檢違規被強制集中檢疫 提告違法拘禁遭駁回","createTime":"2020-12-12T01:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T02:29:57.000Z","uid":216939,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f64d0c925989d14e224ee68384b8fed484d8af1e","tid":2321882,"uid":216939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:15:32.000Z","msg":"台灣公視<br />\n陳奐宇 許政俊 / 高雄報導  2020-12-11 12:56 最後更新：2020-12-11 21:17<br />\n<br />\n香港籍錢姓男子跟台灣女友以及朋友3人，11月22日從香港入境高雄，在住家居家檢疫；但第4天26日就違規，讓朋友開車來接出門吃飯，回來拿手機時被等在門口的衛生局跟警方逮到，隔天強制送去屏東集中檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n高雄市衛生局長黃志中說明：「當事人是返家拿東西的時候，包括我們警察局的警察，包括衛生所人員，也包括里幹事是在門口等他(們)的，所以整個過程裡面，我們希望做到的是防疫上滴水不漏。」<br />\n<br />\n想不到3人被衛生局各罰10萬並集中檢疫後，<strong><span class=\"red\">香港籍男子先是嫌集中檢疫的住所不乾淨，然後又找律師告防疫機關違法拘禁，要求釋放他們</span></strong>，並繼續在家完成居家檢疫，被高雄地院駁回聲請。<br />\n<br />\n高雄市衛生局簡任技正潘炤穎表示：「他們也依據相關的法令進行救濟行為，在法官的判決上面也認知到，基本上在防疫的工作上面我們不分本國外國，基本上都是一律平等的。」<br />\n<br />\n高雄近期居家檢疫人數大增，11月至今社區跟防疫旅館都有部分居家檢疫違規案件，衛生局也提醒民眾，居家檢疫期間只要踏出檢疫場所，就算時間短、沒接觸其他人還是違規，可依違規狀況開罰10萬至100萬罰鍰，希望民眾遵守規定、共同防疫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpKLU7m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpKLU7m.jpg&h=14326c29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.pts.org.tw/article/503952?fbclid=IwAR1GgCta-8lx0n8dWcT3XmBdq9mT1kO9Kig_ywRlaA-zyoZZd2MlK1jWkd4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.pts.org.tw%2Farticle%2F503952%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1GgCta-8lx0n8dWcT3XmBdq9mT1kO9Kig_ywRlaA-zyoZZd2MlK1jWkd4&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmsls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=a30fb6e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.pts.org.tw/article/503952?fbclid=IwAR1GgCta-8lx0n8dWcT3XmBdq9mT1kO9Kig_ywRlaA-zyoZZd2MlK1jWkd4</a><br />\n<br />\n真係丟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔跟防疫就算，仲要告返人地轉頭，人地唔趕你返香港真係偷笑。"},{"pid":"98df1aadc82d0311028c95ebb2e724b83fec86f6","tid":2321882,"uid":11291,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:21:24.000Z","msg":"香港籍男子先是嫌集中檢疫的住所不乾淨，然後又找律師告防疫機關違法拘禁，要求釋放他們<br />\n<br />\n正仆街嚟仲喺度搵藉口"},{"pid":"ed4812ba27a40f12413de331aa4ced01cc1eccfa","tid":2321882,"uid":87576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:23:07.000Z","msg":"我以為非台灣人依家入唔到台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed0daac677cba1f6e27244c536fd953c89910f9","tid":2321882,"uid":167394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:26:53.000Z","msg":"有人想播毒"},{"pid":"ab3657f111ab316534a158a254e1d108b710bd8d","tid":2321882,"uid":154373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:32:56.000Z","msg":"香港人又搞臭人地地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />劣根性無撚得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00280a053b7e5c9aa3b80c9ee293be274b1c167b","tid":2321882,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ab3657f111ab316534a158a254e1d108b710bd8d","tid":2321882,"uid":154373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:32:56.000Z","msg":"香港人又搞臭人地地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />劣根性無撚得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:43:09.000Z","msg":"其實香港人本質同中国人都係一樣, 唔駛份得咁仔細"},{"pid":"0ed247d2abccc34230d80ce5806c53725e14b1ca","tid":2321882,"uid":216939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed4812ba27a40f12413de331aa4ced01cc1eccfa","tid":2321882,"uid":87576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:23:07.000Z","msg":"我以為非台灣人依家入唔到台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:49:54.000Z","msg":"如果你係移民或者居留係可以去台灣"},{"pid":"083d4deee7d1f1f6538d4518771b7d0891bf7af0","tid":2321882,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:51:03.